<h1 class="mb-4"><i class="bi bi-pencil"></i> 编辑类别</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <form action="/categories/edit/<%= category.category_id %>?_method=PUT" method="POST">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="category_name" class="form-label">类别名称 <span class="text-danger">*</span></label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="category_name"
              name="category_name"
              class="form-control"
              value="<%= category.category_name %>"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary me-2">保存修改</button>
            <a href="/categories" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">取消</a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i> 类别信息</h4>
        <p><strong>创建时间：</strong> <%= new Date(category.created_at).toLocaleString() %></p>
        <p><strong>最后更新：</strong> <%= new Date(category.updated_at).toLocaleString() %></p>
        <hr>
        <a href="/items/category/<%= category.category_id %>" class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100">
          <i class="bi bi-collection"></i> 查看此类别的物品
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="card-title text-danger"><i class="bi bi-trash"></i> 删除类别</h4>
        <p>如果该类别下有物品，将无法删除。您需要先修改或删除相关物品。</p>
        <form action="/categories/delete/<%= category.category_id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger w-100" onclick="return confirm('确定要删除此类别吗？如果该类别下有物品，将无法删除。')">
            删除此类别
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>